  hiroshima is best known as the first city in history to be targeted by a nuclear weapon when the united states army air forces ( usaaf ) dropped an atomic bomb on the city at 8:15   a.m. on august 6 , 1945 , near the end of world war ii.   history   sengoku period ( 1589–1871 ) thumb|hiroshima castle   hiroshima was established on the river delta coastline of the seto inland sea in 1589 by the powerful warlord mōri terumoto , who made it his capital after leaving kōriyama castle in aki province .

the days of world war ii : at 8:15 a.m. on the 6th of this month in 1945 , an atomic bomb was dropped on hiroshima

